### 测试数据初始化请求
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

> {% client.global.set("token", response.body.data.token); %}

### 创建案件
POST http://localhost:8080/api/cases
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "caseName": "张三买卖合同纠纷",
  "caseNumber": "CASE2024001",
  "caseType": "民事",
  "caseReason": "买卖合同纠纷",
  "procedure": "一审",
  "court": "北京市朝阳区人民法院",
  "currentStage": "咨询",
  "filingDate": "2026-04-01",
  "deadlineDate": "2026-07-01"
}

### 创建待办
POST http://localhost:8080/api/todos
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "准备张三案件材料",
  "content": "收集合同、付款凭证等证据材料",
  "priority": "high",
  "dueDate": "2026-04-21",
  "status": "pending",
  "relatedType": "case",
  "relatedId": 1
}

### 创建日程
POST http://localhost:8080/api/calendar
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "张三案件庭前会议",
  "calendarType": "hearing",
  "startTime": "2026-04-20T09:00:00",
  "endTime": "2026-04-20T11:00:00",
  "location": "北京市朝阳区人民法院",
  "caseId": 1
}
